{"tid":2507054,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗份大學功課，我形象盡失。。。","createTime":"2021-04-27T17:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T18:59:29.000Z","uid":250222,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"736123906d70b91c61c8b53ec2b0cd477a52ac4a","tid":2507054,"uid":250222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:51:02.000Z","msg":"讀商科，有份功課要整個MVP網站。然後要俾人㩒吓，再用Google Analytics做啲分析。<br />\n咁我嘅ideas嘅功能太過多元化，有好多係個Prof建議用嘅砌website嘅tool都唔夠力整，<br />\n咁冇計，即係我要諗點樣簡單化我個ideas嘅功能，咁我覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n加上我又有返工、其他科嘅嘢要做，所以我就冇點分配時間落去呢份功課度。<br />\n咁就GG了，Deadline就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但我仲未做好個Website，俾時間去俾人㩒入去。<br />\n於是為咗喺短時間內等多啲人㩒入去，我就寫咗個勁on9嘅message去吸引人去㩒<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>Hello 我有份大學功課要整個網站，要用啲流量數據寫報告，希望各位幫手㩒入去睇吓啲pages😘🥰。<br />\n<span class=\"pink\">應該冇人諗到個Website係一個Man到出汁💦嘅男仔整嘅，因為入面啲顏色好少女🌸。</span><br />\n如果可以，請幫我傳一傳開，Deadline將到☠️。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zigmund.softr.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzigmund.softr.io%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0iUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=8144045a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zigmund.softr.io/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你見我個username都知我係一啲低調到不能再低調嘅人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我平時又唔點搞gag，<br />\n所以當我㩒第一個Send時，我內心係掙扎咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n首先係因為我未試過咁樣叫人幫自己，<br />\n第二係因為<span class=\"pink\">戈句嘢</span>，真係好on9，又淫淫地咁，我真係覺得一生人最厚面皮係今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n自問一啲都唔man，識我嘅人都會覺得man同我完全扯唔上關係，所以更加我覺得羞恥。<br />\n我最後都係send咗出去，而且見係group就send。<br />\n成兩年冇講過嘢嘅中同group、2018中大新生group，甚至係公司group全部都有send，全部都係用同一款on9淫 message。<br />\n諗返起，我連好耐冇返嘅教會group都send埋一份，真係乖乖嘅形象冇曬。<br />\n當然仲唔少得Instagram啦，我擺咗上去Story度。<br />\n一諗到要擺喺度24個鐘就頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最後其他group冇人出聲，偏偏公司group老闆就有出聲，問我邊個man到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拖延症嘅後果就係要當小丑，個代價好大呀唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68a1d056c93d4d0efe06f2fa5285400f6e35d8a","tid":2507054,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:55:55.000Z","msg":"冇圖"},{"pid":"6a9692bb552051ce21f5592d25b11b58b8860bfb","tid":2507054,"uid":36383,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"冇圖仲要㩒一條來歷不明嘅 link <br />\n食屎狗，已 report"},{"pid":"d722f9a8ccaa03a09e274bdc6751239ec2c1e43f","tid":2507054,"uid":308662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"你仲開post 果陣見你段野已經笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dd7380d537fb15b1042a410e0ca44f2bfe3979","tid":2507054,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:57:14.000Z","msg":"咁你用左咩野website tool去砌？"},{"pid":"64d2f19f94baa0c449dbe4409a53489052112731","tid":2507054,"uid":394002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"條link有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afb1c05d23082599d1068317423a7848b09159c","tid":2507054,"uid":135967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:57:41.000Z","msg":"幾好啊整得 幫你share咗出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d32b187f52430322fdf7ecf427eca297c6404a","tid":2507054,"uid":24457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:58:21.000Z","msg":"好明顯你唯一send過嘅地方就係呢個post"},{"pid":"05042aee7f014457c26ed0b8f3edf78182889e6d","tid":2507054,"uid":317662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"J圖都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fff05a0518e4391873f2a4d59fd8f5551d28d3","tid":2507054,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi