lyTime":"2021-04-27T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"Illustration 換返真人stock photo<br />\nCategory 㩒邊個都係出咗個堆圖 咁你分嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472529e6d40fc6e4537713920398a93f975ffd69","tid":2507054,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"4f6fa76e3489cee4a67784dca21eb9d09d99b95a","tid":2507054,"uid":250222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65ad43378e337af53b687811ec19ee5ea35996ae","tid":2507054,"uid":341722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"Illustration 換返真人stock photo<br />\nCategory 㩒邊個都係出咗個堆圖 咁你分嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:56:34.000Z","msg":"冇咁多資源去做，所以淨係集中整一個category，咁個prof又接受，因為睇返舊時啲example，佢哋都係差唔多。<br />\n至於illustration/真人stock photo嘅問題，我搵唔到啲高質，睇落去冇咁kam嘅真人圖，所以索性用illustration，同埋參考咗一啲business嘅webpage，佢哋都係用illustration，所以我都唔執著用真人stock photo。"},{"pid":"152a87a23c225bf68fe92835324656cfcdf2e7a1","tid":2507054,"uid":84619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:58:59.000Z","msg":"無J圖 自己好好反省下<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"ea105b65a7cdd5c2e31627a49d73b8058551551c","tid":2507054,"uid":250222,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"圖呀，J圖就冇啦唉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95Pzv19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95Pzv19.jpg&h=32016873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7raOOP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7raOOP.jpg&h=16498447&s={SIZE}\" />"}}